verbose_text: The GWAS curator assigned Experimental Factor Ontology (EFO) 27 was used to filter out non disease phenotypes (e.g., pharmacogenomics responses, etc.) by retaining those under the branch EFO0000408 : disease, reducing the 2,373 GWAS traits to 533 diseases.
